1. for running android emulator devices want to install android studio and java on the mac.
2. and for ios emulator want to install xcode.
3. SafeAreaView only works for the ios devices but not working for android device for also working on android we want to use 'react-native-safe-area-context' this module.
4. '@react-native-async-storage/async-storage' to store data inside mobile device persistent storage to hold access token and those things.
5. 'lodash' for performing js operations.
6. '@react-navigation/native' & '@react-navigation/native-stack' for navigation.
7. 'npm install @react-native-vector-icons/fontisto' for icons in react native cli project.
8. '@react-native-community/datetimepicker' for datepicker and time picker.
9. 'npm install --save react-native-sqlite-storage' this lib used for sqlite db.
10. 





// command to execute after adding new package in react native application
    cd android && ./gradlew clean
    cd ..
    npx react-native run-android